lead_paragraph: The Oklahoma City tandem of Kevin Durant and Russell Westbrook were too much for the New York Knicks to handle on Tuesday as the Thunder won 128-122 in overtime at Madison Square Garden.

headline.print_headline: Durant Scores 44 in Thunder's OT Win at New York
